description: McfbCellProfile: Stores metadata and configuration parameters for a cell's Multi-connectivity Feature Based (MCFB) profile, including its identifier, location, and various operational settings.  dateTime: Timestamp of data collection; Area_Name: Geographic location of the cell; CellId: Unique identifier for the cell; Id2: Duplicate of CellId; Id3:  Ancillary identifier (likely unused); Id4: Another ancillary identifier (likely default value); vsDataType: Data type identifier; vsDataFormatVersion: Version of data format; McfbCellProfile.epsFbAtSessionSetup: Status of EPS fallback at session setup; McfbCellProfile.reservedBy: Reserved field; McfbCellProfile.ueConfGroupType: UE configuration group type; McfbCellProfile.mcfbCellProfileId: MCFB profile identifier.
